title: Googly bits ONLY for Android Eclair 2.0 on Dream/Magic
description:
This zip contains SOME files necessary to get Android 2.0 (aka Eclair) running on your Dream (T-Mobile G1, etc) or Magic 32B (T-Mobile MyTouch3G, etc) devices.  All packages ARE ALREADY SIGNED, so no need to worry about that.  Basic instructions are provided, but if you can't figure it out DON'T ASK HERE.  If you don't know who to ask already, then you shouldn't be trying to install this!!!

The full images that you need, without the googly bits, are available at http://code.google.com/p/android-newreco/downloads/list

Enjoy!
